{"word":"κλίνη","slug":"κλίνη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰλίνη, ης, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κλίνω\">κλίνω</a></el>] of a structure used for lying down, with formal characteristics ranging from stretcher to a more fixed surface, depending on context:<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> stretcher <a href='B:470 9:2'>Mt 9:2</a>, <a href='B:470 9:6'>6</a>; <a href='B:490 5:18'>Lk 5:18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> bed <a href='B:480 4:21'>Mk 4:21</a>; <a href='B:480 7:30'>7:30</a>; <a href='B:480 8:16'>8:16</a>; <a href='B:490 17:34'>Lk 17:34</a>.</b> A <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Heb.\">Heb.</a> idiom underlies <el>βάλλειν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> ϰ.</el> throw into a sickbed<b> <a href='B:730 2:22'>Rv 2:22</a><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> <b>dining couch <a href='B:480 7:4'>Mk 7:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κλινάριον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κλινίδιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}